\intbl \ql \b Background\b0 \line The Milpark Business School is registered with the Department of Higher Education as a private higher education provider and is accredited to offer higher education programmes by the HEQC. The institution has also applied for the Advanced Certificate in Management in the contact mode. \cell \pard 

\intbl \row \pard 
\line \par\pard\trowd\trqc \trpaddl113\trpaddt113\trpaddb113\trpaddr113\trpaddfl3\trpaddft3\trpaddfb3\trpaddfr3\trgaph100\trrh100\trleft36
